						<div class="postbody">Just a minor point, but I would suggest to avoid doing .equ #00000000 and would do .equ 00000000 instead, then put the # in your code.  I know it should work either way, but it's helpful to have your code be as clear as possible that immediate mode is being used (in addition to using all caps for defined constants, like you're doing already).</div>

